    "content" : "Dad has been busy during his trips back to Bristol repairing the front beam hangers...\n<br> \n<br> Dad made a gig to set the correct position of the hangers\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412469.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Then made plates for the sides, see addition strenthener for the weld.\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412471.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412472.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> All in and ready..\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412474.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412475.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> I drove up this weekend to help fit the CE IRS legs, lots of cutting...\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412481.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412482.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412483.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412484.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> One for Si \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":wink:\" title=\"Wink\"> \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":lol:\" title=\"LOL\"> \n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412485.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Test fit...\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412490.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Jig, all nice and square\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412491.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412492.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Test fit gearbox...nice \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_cool.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\"8)\" title=\"Cool\"> \n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412493.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412494.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Bit of paint...\n<br> \n<br> \n<img src=\"http://images.thesamba.com/vw/gallery/pix/412495.jpg\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"Image\">\n<br> \n<br> Now thinking of ditching the solid front mount and going for a mid mount. Once I lowered the front beam it will be time to move the bus down here for more welding before paint \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":P\" title=\"Razz\"> ....it's gotta be low to get in the garage \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_rolleyes.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":roll:\" title=\"Roll Eyes\">",
