    "content" : "<blockquote>\n <div>\n  <cite>Rusting Hulk wrote:</cite>Your such a pansy wearing rubber gloves ($2 trick) and letting that retired bloke do all the hard work for you, at least it will be done properly \n  <img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":wink:\" title=\"Wink\"> Say hello to your Dad for me\n </div>\n</blockquote> \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":lol:\" title=\"LOL\"> \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":lol:\" title=\"LOL\"> \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_lol.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":lol:\" title=\"LOL\"> \n<br> \n<br> Si That retired bloke is doing just fine thanks, he's gone from flat out busy with work to doing nought and taken to it very well indeed. He's not doing any work on the BD he's far too busy going on holiday every other month or two. He does drive up to Bristol now and then to check it's still sat in the garage....but I have free storage until the house sells\n<br> \n<br> I may have found some free parking for the truck (though I have a prospective buyer), plan is to get the BD down here and then I will weld it up! I have found a painter \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_cool.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\"8)\" title=\"Cool\"> Everything takes time and we run at half speed down here on a good day!\n<br> \n<br> Is yours in paint yet.... \n<img class=\"smilies\" src=\"./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" alt=\":wink:\" title=\"Wink\">",
